'''L129A1'''是一款由[[路易斯機械與工具公司|路易斯機械與工具公司（LMT）]]生產的[[SR-25狙擊步槍|SR-25]]規格步槍，設計基於LMT [[LMT_MARS-H步槍|LW308MWS]]。L129A1目前有限地在英軍服役，並將會取代所有[[手動槍機|手動槍機]]操作的[[精密國際AW狙擊步槍|L96A1]]及L118A1。

== 歷史 ==
2009年，[[英國軍隊|英軍]]與其他國家的軍隊一樣在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]遇上[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56 NATO]]步槍威力及射程不足的問題。因此在12月，[[英國國防部|英國國防部]]初步編列150萬[[英镑|英鎊]]作緊急作戰需求合約（{{Lang-en|Urgent Operational Requirements}}）的預算，以尋找一款7.62 NATO口徑，在500-800公尺能有效殺傷的步槍。LMT的LM308MWS在英軍的測試中擊敗了[[黑克勒-科赫|黑克勒-科赫]]的[[HK417自動步槍|HK417]]、[[埃斯塔勒国营工厂|FN]]的[[FN_SCAR突擊步槍|SCAR-H]]、Sabre Defence的XR-10、以及奈特軍械和Oberland Arms的產品，被採用為[[L129A1精確射手步槍|L129A1]]，並透過執法國際（{{Lang-en|Law Enforcement International}}）進口至英國<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Taking Back The Infantry Half-km: Britains L129A1|url=http://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/Taking-Back-The-Infantry-Half-km-Britains-L129A1-06426/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Defense Industry Daily staff|date=2010-06-08|last=|first=|format=|work=Defense Industry Daily|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330135722/https://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/Taking-Back-The-Infantry-Half-km-Britains-L129A1-06426/}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Sharpshooter: The UK’s New L129A1 7.62x51mm Rifle|url=http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/sharpshooter-the-uks-new-l129a1-7-62x51mm-rifle/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Dan Shea|date=2012-01-11|last=|format=|work=Small Arms Defense Journal|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210180805/http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/sharpshooter-the-uks-new-l129a1-7-62x51mm-rifle/}}</ref><ref name=":22">{{Cite web|title=The Lewis Machine & Tool Sharpshooter System – The All-American Commercial Model|url=https://www.ammoland.com/2012/04/the-lewis-machine-tool-sharpshooter-system/|accessdate=2021-02-07|date=2012-04-25|last=Riehl|first=F.|work=AmmoLand.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302075851/https://www.ammoland.com/2012/04/the-lewis-machine-tool-sharpshooter-system/}}</ref>。每個八人小組將獲分配一把L129A1，當中三人會被訓練使用該步槍<ref>{{Cite web|title=British L129A1 sharpshooter rifle|url=https://armamentresearch.com/british-l129a1-sharpshooter-rifle/|accessdate=2021-02-10|date=2017-03-20|format=|work=Armament Research Services|publisher=|language=en-GB|author1=Ian McCollum|author2=N.R. Jenzen-Jones|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127135524/https://armamentresearch.com/british-l129a1-sharpshooter-rifle/}}</ref>。

英國國防部總共採購了440把L129A1。除了作為精確射手步槍，部分L129A1改配上L17A2[[瞄准镜|精確倍率瞄具]]（Schmidt & Bender 3-12x50）及[[SureFire|SureFire]]抑制器，作為狙擊手支援武器（{{Lang-en|'''S'''niper '''S'''upport '''W'''eapon}}，簡稱SSW）使用。

